    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Flint projectile points of the Upper Paleolithic period. These are distinctive arch-backed points characteristic of the Federmesser culture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
